I found the perfect travel companion for my weekend getaway; @victorinoxnorthamerica Spectra 3.0 carry on luggage.

The bold design makes this carry on super stylish-but a big winning factor for me is that it’s also eco-friendly; 65% of the material used to make its exterior shell is recycled polycarbonate.

 It’s lined with an antimicrobial material that keeps everything clean and safe, which is especially important during these times. Plus, the different compartments and openings make packing a breeze, and with its ability to expand up to 20%, I don’t have to worry about that unplanned shopping :) 
 
And the best part? You can personalize your luggage with your choice of scale color and text or message! Where should I go next? ✈️ @victorinoxnorthamerica
